Disk-Drill-iPhone-File-Recovery.jpeg?resize=1200%2C777&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-File-Recovery.jpeg?resize=1536%2C994&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-File-Recovery.jpeg?resize=2048%2C1326&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"777\" loading=\"lazy\" /><figcaption>Disk Drill takes some time to get going, but will find plenty of old data.</figcaption></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>That’s not to say that Disk Drill doesn’t add plenty of features. In my testing, it was able to pull from data I thought was long lost from my iPhone. I will concede it took some time to scan, though, running for around an hour before I could dig into the data.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>I was impressed by how many old Whatsapp messages it could recover, as well as old contact information and more.</p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Disk Drill iPhone Byte to Byte Backup\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 3840w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=300%2C194&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=768%2C497&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=1200%2C777&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=1536%2C994&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=2048%2C1326&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"777\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<figcaption>Disk Drill can create a disk image of your machine.</figcaption>\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Disk Drill iPhone Byte to Byte Backup\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 3840w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=300%2C194&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=768%2C497&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=1200%2C777&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=1536%2C994&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=2048%2C1326&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"777\" loading=\"lazy\" /><figcaption>Disk Drill can create a disk image of your machine.</figcaption></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Disk Drill iPhone Byte to Byte Backup\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 3840w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=300%2C194&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=768%2C497&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=1200%2C777&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=1536%2C994&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Byte-to-Byte-Backup.jpeg?resize=2048%2C1326&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"777\" loading=\"lazy\" /><figcaption>Disk Drill can create a disk image of your machine.</figcaption></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Aside from recovery, Disk Drill offers plenty more tools. Its duplicate finder runs on local storage as well as <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/231363/the-best-cloud-storage-services-for-apple-users-2.html\">cloud-based options like Dropbox or Google Drive</a>, while Data Protection stores a copy of a deleted file in case you need to refer back to it. On the opposite end of the spectrum, it can shred files so that they’re unrecoverable, too.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Alongside that, it can even create a backup macOS boot drive, or a disk image of your entire hard drive – ideal for older Macs with mechanical drives that could fail.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Disk Drill annoyances</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Disk Drill iPhone Scanning\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 3840w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=300%2C194&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=768%2C497&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=1200%2C777&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=1536%2C994&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=2048%2C1326&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"777\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<figcaption>Scanning takes some time.</figcaption>\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Disk Drill iPhone Scanning\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 3840w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=300%2C194&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=768%2C497&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=1200%2C777&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=1536%2C994&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=2048%2C1326&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"777\" loading=\"lazy\" /><figcaption>Scanning takes some time.</figcaption></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Disk Drill iPhone Scanning\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 3840w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=300%2C194&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=768%2C497&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=1200%2C777&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=1536%2C994&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Disk-Drill-iPhone-Scanning.jpeg?resize=2048%2C1326&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 2048w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"777\" loading=\"lazy\" /><figcaption>Scanning takes some time.</figcaption></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Foundry</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Aside from the relatively high price and the time it takes to get a phone scanned, my only real complaint with Disk Drill has been that on occasion it got a little upset when my phone locked itself. On a couple of occasions that ended up stopping the scan dead in its tracks, meaning I needed to start over again. On most of the other occasions, though, this didn’t cause any issues, so it could just have been a bug.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Bottom Line</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>It could be a little expensive for one-off users, but as a safety net for anyone looking to regularly recover data from devices, or for enterprise users, Disk Drill is likely to be a very easy recommendation.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>We also have a round-up of the <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/668874/best-data-recovery-apps-for-mac.html\">best Mac recovery apps</a>. </p>\n\n</div>","author":"","siteTitle":"Macworld","siteHash":"37e84dd5a21fa961d6d6630e269546024dbb7741b2e2fadbe74f47383c70dfbb","entryHash":"bc95f49d3acd671670fd11c65315cdd8f36efbe265563f35dd84bb2300281b12","category":"Apple"}